    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cornflour</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in a large bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>peri peri spice mix</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the juice of <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tofu chunks</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>coated tofu</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>sweetcorn cobettes</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin foil </strong>(or two!)</p><p>Scrunch the <strong>tin foil </strong>around the corn until tightly sealed – this is your <strong>corn parcel[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1694599325549-x200.jpg",
