            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wipe clean the reserved bowl, then add the juice of the <strong>remaining lime</strong>, your <strong>ketchup</strong> and <strong>remaining peri peri spice mix</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>peri peri glaze</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely into rounds</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p>",
