    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything is nearly ready, add the<strong> brioche halves </strong>to the tray[s] with the wedges, then return the tray[s] to the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once everything is ready, add the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>tofu </strong>to the bowl with the peri peri glaze and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>oven baked spicy</strong> <strong>peri peri tofu</strong></p>",
