    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, spread the <strong>warmed brioche base </strong>with your <strong>mayo</strong>, then top with the <strong>sliced tomato </strong>and <strong>oven baked spicy</strong> <strong>peri peri tofu </strong>and top with the <strong>warmed brioche bun lid</strong> – this is your <strong>oven baked spicy peri peri tofu burger</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> wedges </strong>and <strong>sweetcorn cobettes </strong>to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
